<HL> First Capital Plan
To Purchase Unit
Of Hutton Delayed
---
By David B. Hilder
Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal</HL>
<DD> 05/05/87</DD>
<SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO>
<IN> FCH EFH
