   Executive Life
   Restructuring
   Plan Is Proposed
   ---
   California Officials Unveil
   `Rehabilitation' Measure;
   Creditors Facing Losses
   ----
   By Frederick Rose
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/22/91
