<HL>
   Executive Life
   Municipal Pacts
   Are Affirmed
   ---
   `Muni-GIC' Court Decision
   Clouds Elaborate Plans
   To Restructure Insurer
   ----
   By Frederick Rose
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
11/18/91
</DATE>
<SO>
